Package: waymap
Version: 7.2.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, python
Section: web
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://waymapscanner.github.io
Description: Fast Web Vulnerability Scanner and Security Testing Toolkit
 Waymap is a comprehensive web application security scanner for
 SQL Injection, XSS, Command Injection, LFI, CRLF, CORS, Open Redirect,
 API security testing (REST/GraphQL), and WordPress vulnerability scanning.
 Provides automation-friendly scanning with session management.
